overview: Here's one of the books! Alexandra Quinn is on a come back to us. She's more mature and full of fire! She may not be a clinical debutante, but in her own words , "I just wanted to fuck Ed!" So who am I to deprive her? Just Kidding! LOL (Lot Of Laughs). Gauge and Mojo are the couple of the year in my book. She's adorable and eager to please. Nikki, the girl with the hat, is hot too! Her hair was so short she felt more comfortable with that. So who am I to deprive her? She wears a hat!
title: More Dirty Debutantes 129
